Introduction

SUPER JUNIOR-D&E is the duo sub-unit of the male group SUPER JUNIOR, under their own label ODE Entertainment. They debuted on December 16, 2011, with the single "Oppa, Oppa".

On July 14th, it was announced that the members of SUPER JUNIOR-D&E had not renewed their contract with SM Entertainment. However, they will continue to collaborate with the company for SUPER JUNIOR's activities. To continue their future promotions and projects, they established their own label, ODE Entertainment, and both members are co-CEOs.
